<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>A filter stripping all repeated spaces would be useful. Html for example ignores all repeated spaces an just the first is shown.</p>

<p>Such a filter could look like that:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
&lt;?php

require_once 'Zend/Filter/Interface.php';

class Zend_Filter_StripRepeatedSpaces implements Zend_Filter_Interface
{

    public function filter($value)
    {

        return preg_replace('/ +/', ' ', $value);

    }

}

</code></pre>

